[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "ヨハナ……怒ってた、かな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00230",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "怒っていたわけではないと思いまする。\nただ、あれはきっとヨハナの本音――",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00231",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "ヨハナには、アイドルとして成し遂げたい\n強い思いがあるのでございましょう",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00232",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "……イザナには、\nアイドルになって成し遂げたい夢はあるでござるか？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00233",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "夢……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00234",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "突然聞かれても困りますよね。\n……よかったら、少し拙者の話を聞いてくれませぬか？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00235",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "拙者は元々、別の事務所に所属し\n忍者系アイドルとしてソロで活動しておりました",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00236",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "デビュー当時は忍者系という物珍しさからか\n話題になることもありましたが、それも続かず――",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00237",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "ステージを見に来るお客様は日に日に減るばかり。\nやがて事務所をクビになりました",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00238",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "そんな時、社長殿に声をかけられ、\n今こうしているのでございます",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00239",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "そうだったんだ……\n鬼門は、どうしてずっとアイドルを続けているの？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00240",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "元々アイドルを目指した理由は、\n実家を見返したいという思いからでございました",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00241",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "忍びの末裔である我が家には古いしきたりが多く、\n拙者はそれに縛られるのが嫌で家出したのでございます",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00242",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "アイドルになって、忍術で新しい楽しさを生み出し、\n実家を見返してやろうというのが拙者の夢でした",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00243",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "でした……？　ってことは、今は違うの？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00244",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "いえ！　今もその気持ちはありまする。\nただ、新しい夢ができたのです",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00245",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "これはファンレターでございます",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00246",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "ファンレター……ファンの人からのお手紙？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00247",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "はい。拙者が最初にデビューした頃から、\nこまめに送ってくれるファンの方がいるのでござる",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00248",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "こんな拙者を応援してくれている方がいる……\n拙者はこの応援に、たくさんの力をもらいました",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00249",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "そして、その気持ちにアイドルとして応えたいと\n思うのでござる。それが今の拙者の夢でございまする！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00250",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "鬼門の夢……素敵だね！\n聞かせてくれて、ありがとう！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00251",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "とはいえ、今のままでは期待に応えるどころか\n拙者らの生活もままなりませぬから……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00252",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "早く人気アイドルになって、\nちゃんと食べていけるようになりたいですな～……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00253",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]